Queries

aggregateComment

Response

Returns an AggregateComment

Arguments
Name Description
where - CommentWhereInput
orderBy - [CommentOrderByWithRelationInput]
cursor - CommentWhereUniqueInput
take - Int
skip - Int

Example

Query
query AggregateComment(
  $where: CommentWhereInput,
  $orderBy: [CommentOrderByWithRelationInput],
  $cursor: CommentWhereUniqueInput,
  $take: Int,
  $skip: Int
) {
  aggregateComment(
    where: $where,
    orderBy: $orderBy,
    cursor: $cursor,
    take: $take,
    skip: $skip
  ) {
    _count {
      id
      message
      userId
      postId
      commentedAt
      createdAt
      updatedAt
      _all
    }
    _avg {
      id
      userId
      postId
    }
    _sum {
      id
      userId
      postId
    }
    _min {
      id
      message
      userId
      postId
      commentedAt
      createdAt
      updatedAt
    }
    _max {
      id
      message
      userId
      postId
      commentedAt
      createdAt
      updatedAt
    }
  }
}
Variables
{
  "where": CommentWhereInput,
  "orderBy": [CommentOrderByWithRelationInput],
  "cursor": CommentWhereUniqueInput,
  "take": 123,
  "skip": 123
}
Response
{
  "data": {
    "aggregateComment": {
      "_count": CommentCountAggregateOutputType,
      "_avg": CommentAvgAggregateOutputType,
      "_sum": CommentSumAggregateOutputType,
      "_min": CommentMinAggregateOutputType,
      "_max": CommentMaxAggregateOutputType
    }
  }
}
